  "time_ut": 1658624568,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0db3\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d8b\u0dab: \u0d9c\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0dba \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Monkey flu: a global emergency",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The World Health Organization has decided to declare a global emergency regarding the 'monkey fever' (monkeypox) virus.",
        "The World Health Organization took this decision as of yesterday (23) when more than 65,000 people infected with 'monkey fever' were reported from 75 countries. The announcement of the World Health Organization further states that the spread of 'monkey flu' can be considered as a public health emergency.",
        "Although cases of 'monkey flu' virus have been reported from around the world, no deaths have been reported yet. Two cases of 'monkey fever' have been reported from neighboring India. Indian health authorities have said that both of them are residents of Kerala state.",
        "American medical researchers have revealed that the spread of 'monkey flu' mostly occurs among homosexuals, and 95 percent of the spread of the virus is sexual. The country's media reports that the spread of 'monkey fever' in the United States is severe, and the American government has started giving immunization shots for 'monkey fever' at the state level.",
        "'Monkey fever' is a virus commonly seen in Central and West Africa. This is similar to chicken pox. Protection against 'monkey flu' is given by an immunization of the type given to protect against the chicken pox virus.",
        "The World Health Organization has clarified that although one or two cases of 'monkey fever' have been found outside Africa on several occasions, the spread of the 'monkey fever' virus has never been so severe.",
        "The main symptom of 'monkey fever' is fever and skin blisters. 'Monkey fever' is not a serious disease and the disease may heal quickly or develop complications, depending on the body's immunity.",
        "There are two variants of the 'monkey flu' virus. The most severe variety is the 'Congo' variety. This has been identified for the first time in the Congo. The other 'monkey fever' strain is the 'West African monkey fever' strain. It has been confirmed that this 'West African monkey fever' is spreading in Great Britain and America.",
        "The 'monkey flu' virus was first identified in 1958 from the bodies of African monkeys. That is why it is called 'monkey fever'. Not only monkeys, this virus spreads to humans through mammals such as rats, mice, squirrels, etc."
      ],
